{% import "components/projects.njk" as projects %}

<div class="px-4 py-8 my-8 text-center">
  <h2 class="font-serif text-5xl text-nord3">Empire Uncut</h2>
</div>

<div class="max-w-4xl px-4 mx-auto">
  <article>
  <p>
    In 2012, my coworker <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/electronicsworkshop/">Tim Ayers</a> and I took part in Empire Uncut, a fan
    recreation of Empire Strikes Back. The movie was sliced up into 15 second
    segments, and thousands of participants from across the globe picked a scene
    and created it using whatever style they liked!
  </p>
  <p>
    Read more about Empure Uncut and watch the finished film (plus the original
    Star Wars Uncut) at
    <a href="http://starwarsuncut.com/empire"
      >starwarsuncut.com/empire</a
    >.
  </p>
  <h3>Our Scenes</h3>
  <p>
    Tim and I chose two back-to-back scenes, so that we could double our chances
    of getting picked, but only have to work on one set of characters and
    backgrounds.
  </p>
  <p>This is a screenshot of the scene from the original film:</p>
  <img
    class="w-full mb-4"
    src="/static/images/projects/empire-uncut/scene.jpg"
    loading="lazy"
/>
  <p>Here is the combined video of the scenes that we filmed:</p>
  <div class="w-full mb-4">
    <div class="relative aspect-wide">
      <iframe
        src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/Sfc5woaKnlo"
        ref="video"
        width="560"
        height="315"
        class="absolute top-0 left-0 object-cover w-full h-full"
        frameborder="0"
        allow="accelerometer; autoplay; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture"
        allowfullscreen
        loading="lazy"
      ></iframe>
    </div>
  </div>
  <h3>Behind the Scenes Photos</h3>
  <div class="flex flex-wrap mb-4 -m-1">
    {% for photo in empire_uncut %}
      <div class="w-1/2 p-1 border-2 border-white md:w-1/3 hover:border-nord9">
        <a
        class="relative block aspect-wide thumb"
        data-id="{{ photo.id }}"
        data-caption="{{ photo.caption }}"
        data-modal="gallery"
        href="/static/images/projects/empire-uncut/{{ photo.id }}.jpg"
      >
          <img
          src="/static/images/projects/empire-uncut/thumbs/{{ photo.id }}.jpg"
          class="absolute top-0 left-0 object-cover w-full h-full"
          loading="lazy"
/>
        </a>
      </div>
    {% endfor %}
  </div>
  </article>
</div>

<div
  class="fixed inset-0 z-50 flex items-center justify-center hidden js-modal-container"
  data-modal="gallery"
>
  {{ '/src/loader.svg' | svgContents | safe }}
  <button
    class="fixed top-0 right-0 m-4 text-3xl text-white fill-current"
    id="modal-btn-close"
  >
    {{ '/src/icons/icon-x.svg' | svgContents | safe }}
  </button>
  <img src="" class="hidden max-w-2xl js-modal-image"/>
</div>
